 the complete process<br>\n\u2705 Free Q&amp;A session for online and offline students<br>\n<br>\nThings We Cover in Our Indoor Farming Training:<br>\n\ud83d\udccc Cultivation Process<br>\n\ud83d\udd39 Potato Dextrose (PD) preparation<br>\n\ud83d\udd39 Potato Dextrose Agar (PDA) preparation<br>\n\ud83d\udd39 Liquid media preparation<br>\n\ud83d\udd39 Liquid culture preparation<br>\n\ud83d\udd39 Substrate preparation<br>\n\ud83d\udd39 Inoculation<br>\n\ud83d\udd39 Autoclaving<br>\n\ud83d\udd39 Incubation<br>\n\ud83d\udd39 Incubation management<br>\n\ud83d\udd39 Monitoring<br>\n\ud83d\udd39 Harvesting methods<br>\n\ud83d\udd39 Bacterial control<br>\n\ud83d\udd39 Lab environment management<br>\n\ud83d\udd39 Packaging<br>\n\ud83d\udd39 Business model<br>\n\ud83d\udd39 Startup guidance and support<br>\n\ud83d\udd39 Q&amp;A session<\/p>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-769cb849\" data-id=\"769cb849\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\" data-settings=\"{&quot;animation&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2f9ce68e animated-slow elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"2f9ce68e\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_animation&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1065\" height=\"939\" src=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/www.orangeherb.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/image-5.png?fit=1065%2C939&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-image-2027\" alt=\"indoor farming training\" srcset=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/www.orangeherb.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/202